{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013T8Gbe7swGcUGykFVXiPFg","type":"tool_result","content":"<system-reminder>This memory is 5 days old. Memories are point-in-time observations, not live state — claims about code behavior or file:line citations may be outdated. Verify against current code before asserting as fact.</system-reminder>\n     1→---\n     2→name: Backend DB & migration patterns\n     3→description: How migrations work, DB client location, schema config, and existing table inventory — avoids re-searching every time\n     4→type: reference\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→## Migration System\n     8→\n     9→| What | Path |\n    10→|------|------|\n    11→| Migration files | `services/backend/migrations/NNN_snake_name.sql` |\n    12→| Migration runner | `services/backend/src/migrate.ts` |\n    13→| DB client + queries | `services/backend/src/db.ts` |\n    14→| DB config (schema) | `services/backend/src/db-config.ts` |\n    15→| Connection library | `postgres` v3.4.0 (tagged template literals) |\n    16→\n    17→**Naming**: `NNN_description.sql`, zero-padded sequential (001, 002, ...).\n    18→\n    19→**Auto-run**: `pnpm start` = `tsx src/migrate.ts && tsx src/index.ts` — migrations run before server.\n    20→\n    21→**Manual**: `cd services/backend && pnpm migrate` / `pnpm migrate:status`.\n    22→\n    23→**Runner logic**: reads `migrations/` dir, parses version from filename prefix, tracks in `_migrations` table, applies pending in `sql.begin()` transactions. Idempotent.\n    24→\n    25→**Schema support**: `DB_SCHEMA` env var (defaults to `public`). Appends `?options=-csearch_path=<schema>` to connection URL.\n    26→\n    27→## Current Tables (as of migration 006)\n    28→\n    29→| Table | PK | Purpose |\n    30→|-------|----|---------|\n    31→| `rounds` | `pda` | Commit-reveal rounds (coinflip + lord). Key cols: `creator`, `winner`, `settle_tx`, `amount_lamports`, `match_id`, `phase`, `game` |\n    32→| `closecall_rounds` | `round_id` | Pari-mutuel rounds. Entries in JSONB: `green_entries`/`red_entries` = `[{ player, amountLamports }]` |\n    33→| `operator_events` | `id` (BIGSERIAL) | Audit log: `event_type` + JSONB `payload` |\n    34→| `auth_challenges` | `nonce` | JWT challenge nonces |\n    35→| `refresh_tokens` | `id` (BIGSERIAL) | JWT refresh token families |\n    36→| `closecall_candles` | `minute_ts` | Cached Hermes BTC prices |\n    37→\n    38→## Settlement Write Paths\n    39→\n    40→| Game | File | Context |\n    41→|------|------|---------|\n    42→| Coinflip + Lord | `src/worker/settle-tx.ts` | After `settle_confirmed` operator event |\n    43→| Close Call | `src/worker/closecall-settle.ts` | After settle confirmation |\n    44→| Join detection | `src/worker/pda-watcher.ts` (coinflip/lord), `src/routes/closecall.ts` (bet route) |\n    45→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EsZ149HxsCGBH7ihZWCDXq","session_id":"22eabd0a-3a3b-489d-bc57-d8e8d222d116","uuid":"163eb9de-4dd2-4a12-9da8-ee486b24b89c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T21:23:43.798Z"}
